_json.gridTitle: Paul Washer - The Gift Nobody Wants (FULL)
_json.description: Paul Washer - The Gift Nobody Wants (FULL) Paul preaches a message not many want to hear. His is a rock solid teaching on what it means to be  a true believer who bears good fruit, and who has a life pattern of a repentant heart. the work and evidence of a true believer is that he/she is confessional and is a new creation. A changed heart that had an encounter and continues to have encounters with a fierce and awesome God. Paul is refreshingly confrontational, which may offend you..but save you.
